{"tid":1801934,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽] 唔好再講和你shop要靜靜地做, 和你shop要嬴只需一樣野: 人數","createTime":"2019-12-29T04:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T08:51:55.000Z","uid":37722,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1166254718030468ebfefc8244eb5c5241d522f7","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"今日唔知咩事出面係咁吹風叫人和你shop個陣靜d, 9行就得架啦, 可見大家都未明而家和你shop個問題出左係邊<br />\n<br />\n和你shop個本質同和你塞, 甚至同平時開花既原理一樣, 都係人數取決一切. 點解第一次和你塞咁成功? 因為有幾萬人一齊塞. 而家你叫人和你shop個陣靜d, 唔好叫口號, d人點聚人? 人都聚唔到仲點shop?<br />\n<br />\n就我咁多次和你shop既觀察所見, 和你shop我地唯一輸既就係部份和理非連行街都驚埋, 行動力極低連呢種方式都唔出黎, 結果得返行動派肯幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和你shop既攻略根本只需要我地最原始既策略: 人數取決行動, 而家我大概做個基本策略, 細節可以修改:<br />\n<br />\n- 人數少過200人: 全部唔好black bloc, 叫幾次口號聚完人之後純粹行街, 唔好做任何破壞性行為(包括拍窗), 唔好塞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 人數200 - 500人: 可以black bloc, 但如果black bloc人數至少要200人, 行街叫口號聚更多人, 可以舉旗, 可以去藍店參觀, 避免破壞性行為(包括拍窗), 最重要一樣野: 開始要小心便衣狗, 可行情況下就捉便衣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 人數500 - 3000人: black bloc, 口號, 參觀, 舉旗, 做野自由度大好多, 但謹記一點, 商場多數店舖一收鋪就即刻要走, 唔好留<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 3000人以上: 做咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家記住一點, 而家抗爭任何有效方式都一定有人損傷, 人地9拉你點防? 我地一退再退就只係得返係屋企9叫當抗爭呢個選擇. 呢場運動只差2樣野我地就嬴, 勇氣同意志力. 你驚唔出黎, 就輸左成個香港, 最後就集中營相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a93c958e90072e069b99e987b6efd55ef938ce2","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家認同請幫推"},{"pid":"08ab493e638722eb5e44a2c7a7aa52fa5299311b","tid":1801934,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"今日有集會啊 大家記得要去啊 熱門一個Po都冇 完全唔夠宣傳 樓主可唔可以頂置呢段嘢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fba1CHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffba1CHM.jpg&h=b7426169&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"227f77d3032197d4e66b52867898e0ad49454379","tid":1801934,"uid":102713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0d399a78ae38cf3eee6adb0ed79a46e84d323ea","tid":1801934,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:57.000Z","msg":"夠多人 又彩虹戰衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db24ebae6a11b9ef7d00415cdd0d22935c091729","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ab04ea76cf8845797737999f532e0f49cdcc22c","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a7c111c697667a2eead8ff29759901deaf43316","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:13:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f285b0991a64ad7fc658604febf713f68039da86","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e7c30af3c818f42b5d80df23aa611534f3123ab","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cd1cd76698a7dd43541c0b0ac86605ebb19b46","tid":1801934,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse